{"tid":1564992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國瑜：會用「洪荒之力」努力改變台灣命運","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:40:40.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40ff455eab48f8ce4ad730548bab7e4f4666fbd9","tid":1564992,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"鴻海前董事長郭台銘12日上午宣布即日起退出中國國民黨。國民黨總統參選人韓國瑜競選辦公室回應，「對於郭台銘董事長做出這樣的決定，我們表示萬分的遺憾和失望。」<br />\n<br />\n韓競辦並指出，「韓國瑜市長身為中國國民黨提名的總統候選人，會用盡洪荒之力，和所有黨內志同道合的夥伴，一起努力改變台灣的命運，並且推動國民黨的改革和轉型。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/1703524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F1703524&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=236c3179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/1703524</a>"},{"pid":"f0b3ed16259b7df983ca5c422a8e313855517924","tid":1564992,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6f331bdae4d5f3b968a88246866779803946870a","tid":1564992,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:34:34.000Z","msg":"你跳101都唔得洪荒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"